{"tid":1701502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動】追究律政司責任 破壞法治 縱容黑警!!!","createTime":"2019-11-09T06:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T23:32:19.000Z","uid":126366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3190dd37834dcd6f4ad27754c7fcf8e15d56a9","tid":1701502,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T06:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQpiEQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQpiEQF.jpg&h=0826e541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簡介</span></span></strong><br />\n當共匪黑狗藍屍改變策略，針對我哋既和理非既時候。<br />\n我哋都應該<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">開始針對番對家既和理非 - <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">律政司</span>。</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUs7Hk6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUs7Hk6.jpg&h=11cac705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPhoto By 文子言木<br />\n<br />\n唔好以爲<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>律政司</strong></span>係冷氣房就冇殺傷力。<br />\n防暴黑狗夠膽咁惡，就正正係律政司呢班<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">檢控官對佢哋既犯法行爲不作檢控!</span></span></strong><br />\n但就躲藏係班狗後面去針對我哋既手足: <br />\n<strong>1) 7.28 中上環衝突 港大生<span style=\"color: red;\">藏伸縮警棍 判囚6周</span> </strong>: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2oXeffF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oXeffF&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=cc4d0d74\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2oXeffF</a><br />\n<strong>2) 涉改裝雨傘 15 歲男童兩罪罪成 <span style=\"color: red;\">裁判官臨時改控罪</span> 指雷射筆本非攻擊性武器 但被告有意圖照射警</strong>: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Np010d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Np010d&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=ba909824\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Np010d</a><br />\n<strong>3) <span style=\"color: red;\">朱凱廸</span>涉 5.11 會議衝突<span style=\"color: red;\">被捕</span> 朱助理岑敖暉稱 <span style=\"color: red;\">警向律師指朱凱廸不需律師協助</span></strong>: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/34NmdY3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34NmdY3&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=78018561\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34NmdY3</a><br />\n<strong>4) 警改列企圖謀殺 律師：<span style=\"color: red;\">檢控親疏有別</span></strong>: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/32shbyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32shbyA&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=184ea4db\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32shbyA</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">常見問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>問: </strong>爲什麽<strong><ins>律政司檢控官</ins></strong>如此重要? 我可以以市民身份去告班黑狗嗎?<br />\n<strong>答: </strong>法律上並<strong><ins>沒有規定</ins></strong>刑事檢控權只落在政府部門身上，亦即公眾或個人在原則上也有權作出私人刑事檢控。<br />\n但由於檢控過程和司法過程中<strong><ins>所涉及的高昂成本</ins></strong>，和缺乏政府部門所擁有的調查案件的人力、資源和特權，所以實際上，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">私人刑事檢控幾乎並不存在</span></ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問: </strong>我地要攻擊律政司<strong><ins>哪一點?</ins></strong><br />\n<strong>答: </strong>《基本法》第63條規定: <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">香港特別行政區律政司主管刑事檢察工作，不受任何干涉</span></ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>問: </strong>邊個<strong><ins>干涉咗律政司檢控</ins></strong>?<br />\n<strong>答: </strong>根據立場新聞7月30日的報導【怒不可遏】律政司刑事檢控科律師公開信 促政府明確撤回條例 <strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">明示內部有政治壓力</span></ins></strong>: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2qj2ssg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qj2ssg&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOI429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=cebf5be9\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2qj2ssg</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n公開信有最少兩名事檢控科高級律師提供工作證證明，信中指「很多同事」同樣支持市民 ，更明示檢控官職責是保持中立，<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">除了檢控權力，「同樣有不檢控的權力」</span></ins></strong>，在這段時期「外界以至內部」都令同事有很大的<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">政治壓力</span></ins></strong>，但他們會儘量堅守中立原則，每一宗案件都只考慮證據是否充分，是否符合公眾利益，「絕不考慮被告的背景和政治傾向」。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>問: </strong>所以<strong><ins>打壓檢控官</ins></strong>既<ins><strong>共匪同鄭若驊</strong></ins>，係我地針對既目標?<br />\n<strong>答: </strong>無錯，戴耀庭曾就<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>律政司司長角色利益衝</ins></span></strong>突提醒我們，&quot;按香港的本地法律，律政司司長是律政司之首，所有律政人員都是他的下屬，包括了刑事檢控專員。<br />\n因此，<strong><ins>刑事檢控的決定</ins></strong>理論上<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">最終都是由律政司司長來做的</span></ins></strong>。<br />\n正是由於律政司司長的<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">角色衝突</span></em></strong>，既是政治任命的官員但又應獨立地進行刑事檢控的決定，令人合理地懷疑律政司司長無可避免地在一些政治敏感的案件，會受到政治因素影響，結果是<strong><ins>犠牲了法治</ins></strong>的要求。&quot;<br />\n言論發生在反送中前，但早有預見今時今日黑狗夥同鄭若驊毀滅香港法治!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11/18 1PM - 2PM<br />\n太古廣場中庭 (近AMC戲院)<br />\n約定你!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"457d6bb7e0834bdf6b2b0585ea095838e1761c29","tid":1701502,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T23:32:19.000Z","msg":"由於抗爭運動出現新變化<br />\n此活動已經取消"}]}